<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<FindBugsFilter xmlns="https://github.com/spotbugs/filter/3.0.0">
  <!--
    Reviewed suppressions (Chapter 16: suppress with a reason, never disable a whole detector).

    This module has NONE: that is the chapter's point made by the build. The metric models are
    immutable records, the rollout policy copies its baseline and ratchet inputs defensively, and the
    dashboard spec exposes only unmodifiable views, so the representation-exposure detectors stay
    quiet without any suppression. The filter is kept (empty) so a future, genuinely-reviewed
    suppression has a home with a reason, rather than being added inline.
  -->
</FindBugsFilter>
